New-Item .dockerignore -ItemType File
```

Open `.dockerignore` and paste:
```
# Virtual Environment
venv/
.venv/

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.pdb

# Git
.git/
.gitignore

# Environment files
.env
*.env

# Streamlit cache
.streamlit/

# Test files
tests/
*.test.py

# Dev files
*.ipynb
*.md
!README.md

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log